snippet.title: EVE Online - Eclipse Quadrant 2 Trailer
snippet.description:
EVE Online's Quadrant 2 is called Eclipse and its arrival is imminent! Kicking off on 6 April, the overall theme will revolve around shifting the balance of power in New Eden. Play EVE for free -https://bit.ly/play_eve

Eclipse will bring events, celebrations, login campaigns, visual updates, huge balance changes, new and mysterious ships and weapons, as well as the final chapter of the Invasion expansion to EVE Online.

Music & Sound Design: Makewaves Audio 

For past, present and future of EVE Online visit https://bit.ly/updates_eve
Influence the outcome of a star-spanning conflict - https://bit.ly/eve_eclipse
